OL,3,C#260m and three years later - will
OL,4,Cthis road solve Carlisle's traffic
OL,5,Cproblems?
OL,7,FA new bypass linking the M6 with west
OL,8,FCumbria has officially opened, in what
OL,9,Fcouncil leaders have described as a
OL,10,F"historic moment" for the region.
OL,12,FThe so-called Carlisle Southern Link
OL,13,FRoad opened to traffic on Friday (12
OL,14,FJune) following a ceremony marking the
OL,15,Fcompletion of one of the largest
OL,16,Finfrastructure projects delivered in
OL,17,FCumberland in recent years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
