OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781273476
OL,3,C#260m and three years later - will
OL,4,Cthis road solve Carlisle's traffic
OL,5,Cproblems?
OL,7,FThe new 5 mile route connects Junction
OL,8,F42 of the M6 with the A595, creating a
OL,9,Fnew link across the south of Carlisle.
OL,10,FThis should help reduce congestion,
OL,11,Fimprove journey times and support
OL,12,Ffuture development, including the
OL,13,Fproposed St Cuthbert's Garden Village.
OL,15,FThe bypass cost #259.4 million,
OL,16,Fincluding #246 million from Homes
OL,17,FEngland, and has been under
OL,18,Fconstruction since June 2023.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
