CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781273476
OL,3,C#260m and three years later - will
OL,4,Cthis road solve Carlisle's traffic
OL,5,Cproblems?
OL,7,FOver the three-year project, more than
OL,8,Fone million cubic metres of material
OL,9,Fwere moved, while engineers built
OL,10,Fthree road bridges, six footbridges
OL,11,Fand four new roundabouts. More than
OL,12,F14km of walking, cycling and wheeling
OL,13,Froutes have also been created
OL,14,Falongside the road.
OL,16,FCumberland Councillor Denise Rollo
OL,17,Fsaid: "The opening of the Carlisle
OL,18,FSouthern Link Road is a fantastic
OL,19,Fmilestone and a truly historic moment
OL,20,Ffor Cumberland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
