CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781273476
OL,3,C#260m and three years later - will
OL,4,Cthis road solve Carlisle's traffic
OL,5,Cproblems?
OL,7,F"This is one of the most significant
OL,8,Finfrastructure projects we've
OL,9,Fdelivered, and it will make a lasting
OL,10,Fdifference to how people travel,
OL,11,Fconnect and do business across the
OL,12,Farea.
OL,14,F"Homes England, which provided the
OL,15,Fmajority of the funding, said the road
OL,16,Fwould help unlock land for thousands
OL,17,Fof new homes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
