OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781273476
OL,3,C#260m and three years later - will
OL,4,Cthis road solve Carlisle's traffic
OL,5,Cproblems?
OL,7,FPauline Schaffer, from Homes England,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The opening of the Carlisle
OL,9,FSouthern Link Road is a significant
OL,10,Fmoment for transport in the region and
OL,11,Ffor the thousands of new homes that
OL,12,Fcan now be delivered at St Cuthbert's
OL,13,FGarden Village.
OL,15,F"The project was delivered by
OL,16,FGalliford Try, which said the road
OL,17,Fwould leave a lasting legacy through
OL,18,Fimproved connectivity and future
OL,19,Finvestment opportunities.
